				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/Chinh-o%C3%A1n/poem-QUMfE9cgJPhd21pFnymwXw">Chinh oán - 征怨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Giang-Y%C3%AAm/author-BvX7SZcYDh6BIaZimIwj-Q">Giang Yêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/Du-th%C3%A0nh-nam-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-th%E1%BB%A7-L%E1%BA%A1c-hoa/poem-uOsbHUTtzjVmTBa94tAKkQ">Du thành nam thập lục thủ - Lạc hoa - 遊城南十六首－落花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-D%C5%A9/author-mXDKUZpgHTE66OhltBCLIw">Hàn Dũ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/H%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-v%C5%A9-trung-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-x%C3%A1-nh%C3%A2n-%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bc-du-Thi%C3%AAn-Tr%C3%BAc-%C4%91%E1%BA%AFc-th%E1%BA%ADp-l%E1%BB%A5c-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-tr%C3%ACnh-L%E1%BB%A5c-V%E1%BB%A5-Quan/poem-y3W-BVF3ClTEkWa3QK-EcQ">Hàn thực vũ trung, đồng xá nhân ước du Thiên Trúc đắc thập lục tuyệt cú trình Lục Vụ Quan - 寒食雨中同舍人約遊天竺得十六絕句呈陸務觀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/author-JSRpfYAHfq-c4bVKwnYGVg">Dương Vạn Lý</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/Li%E1%BB%85u/poem-IHS4McxsT8hyObFCyO-dhQ">Liễu - 柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%C3%A0n-%E1%BB%90c/author-wyu82iSv-bH9msUkq5vWDQ">Hàn Ốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/Ph%C3%B3-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-L%C6%B0-qu%E1%BA%ADn-Ho%C3%A0i-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-ng%E1%BB%99-phong/poem-Musz9yRgydj13JyqeFRBEw">Phó Đồng Lư quận Hoài thượng ngộ phong - 赴桐廬郡淮上遇風</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Tr%E1%BB%8Dng-Y%C3%AAm/author-V2PfiYxdyB2eEu42wOrwSw">Phạm Trọng Yêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/Thi%C3%AAm-t%E1%BB%B1-th%C3%A1i-tang-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-7-VP88VbG65jmTavv3gmUQ">Thiêm tự thái tang tử - 添字采桑子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Thanh-Chi%E1%BA%BFu/author-6q8syMJi1LKPt3rH8HfbQQ">Lý Thanh Chiếu</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/Thu%E1%BB%B3-li%E1%BB%85u/poem-R-k0vYS_OEy97lSR83Q1_Q">Thuỳ liễu - 垂柳</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/author-0IgWRHCvEyX64lV-HaskRg">Đường Ngạn Khiêm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%91ng-Gi%E1%BA%A3-c%C3%A1c-l%C3%A3o-xu%E1%BA%A5t-Nh%E1%BB%AF-Ch%C3%A2u/poem-wMiJs_Ug9qzG_gr6Vxvswg">Tống Giả các lão xuất Nhữ Châu - 送賈閣老出汝州</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BB%B1-qu%C3%A2n-chi-xu%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%B9/poem-BlRsjRF4NmZyLHFA9sN37w">Tự quân chi xuất hỹ - 自君之出矣</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BB%A9-t%C3%B9ng/poem-gGXMjqTTUrdwriPEB0cMQw">Tứ tùng - 四松</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br></div>	</div>
